title: Front Set-backs from the Street Line/Plot Boundary and set- backs from the zonal boundary in the different zones shall be as in Table No 18hereunder
clause_text: Front Set-backs from the Street Line/Plot Boundary and set- backs from the zonal boundary in the different zones shall be as in Table No 18hereunder. Front set-back from Street Line/Plot Boundary (in meters) ** Refer to sub-Regulations 41(2) (ii)of this Regulations.
